Interface Signature.RefTypeSig

All Superinterfaces:
Signature
All Known Subinterfaces:
Signature.ArrayTypeSig, Signature.ClassTypeSig, Signature.TypeVarSig
Enclosing interface:
Signature
public static sealed interface Signature.RefTypeSig extends Signature permits Signature.ArrayTypeSig, Signature.ClassTypeSig, Signature.TypeVarSig
Models the signature of a reference type, which may be a class, interface, type variable, or array type.
See Java Language Specification:
4.3 Reference Types and Values
See Java Virtual Machine Specification:
4.7.9.1 Signatures
